        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI note that this updated code continues to use 2 spaces for indents instead of the 4 spaces stipulated here: https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Java+code+style\nShould we be updating the Java code style as we go? Or will there be a single commit to fix all of this at the same time? I wonder who could answer this last question!",
